# NOTE: certs/fairplay/* is NOT ignored here. The build seeds placeholder
# FairPlay certs (copies of the public certs/legacy-fairplay/fairplay.{crt,pem})
# into certs/fairplay/ at the expected names so activation.rs can
# include_bytes!() them at compile time. The real Apple keys are never present;
# only these public placeholders ship in this vendored tree.
